{"tid":667142,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)乒乓情人夢 特務型戰 遺落戰境","createTime":"2018-05-16T13:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T16:57:37.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8708975e2c2dca3c728ca87b5ba9c657c6c70614","tid":667142,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T13:15:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=8jmk2lYNBG50uK1ZiHh80o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=6b331018\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=8jmk2lYNBG50uK1ZiHh80o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=fd0c5d81\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=8jmk2lYNBG50uK1ZiHh80o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=9037461c\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"http://userdisk.webry.biglobe.ne.jp/030/815/48/N000/000/013/150142425188269933179.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fuserdisk.webry.biglobe.ne.jp%2F030%2F815%2F48%2FN000%2F000%2F013%2F150142425188269933179.jpg&h=51fbeac9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/0/01/The_Man_from_U.N.C.L.E._Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F0%2F01%2FThe_Man_from_U.N.C.L.E._Poster.jpg&h=221fe847&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/2/2e/Oblivion2013Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F2%2F2e%2FOblivion2013Poster.jpg&h=c1ae09d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.桌球女神童富田多滿子，在母親去世後放棄桌球，後來因為男友變心，加上挽救母親創立的「花花桌球會」，重拾桌球拍，並且夥拍退役拳手荻原久，參加全國桌球大賽神奈川縣預選賽<br />\n<br />\n2.故事背景定於1960年代冷戰時期，敘述隸屬於美國CIA特務拿破崙&middot;蘇洛（亨利&middot;卡維爾飾）和前蘇聯KGB特務伊利亞&middot;科里亞金（艾米&middot;漢默飾）被迫合作並受命執法聯合指揮部「紳士局（The Man from U.N.C.L.E.）」阻止一個神秘的國際犯罪組織，以免核武器造成全球性的災難，甚至引發第三次世界大戰.......<br />\n<br />\n3.2017年，未知的外星機器「三角錐體」入侵地球掌控世界，將地球兩名精英Harper和Olsen大量複製並植入記憶，虛構了一個2077年地球戰勝外星人後，地球已不適居住，人類移居泰坦星的情節。Jack Harper（湯姆&middot;克魯斯飾）擔任駐紮在地球49號塔台的維修技師，負責維護抽取海水的機器。Victoria Olsen擔任通訊官及Harper之妻，負責和地球軌道上的「四面體」太空站連絡。兩人來地球前都基於安全因素被洗掉了記憶，但Harper時常夢見自己和一位女子在一橦大樓上。少數存活的外星人則仍不放棄奪掠地球的剩餘資源<br />\n<br />\n9 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=8jmk2lYNBG50uK1ZiHh80o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=8ee25d14\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=8jmk2lYNBG50uK1ZiHh80o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=38db27a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab88a8de16e9c13c3c349bd11f373705c3896d07","tid":667142,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T13:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9629b9daaee9481d0028e33b6f2159635e9d92b","tid":667142,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T13:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加插播左黐筋雙響炮先<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9a/The_Nice_Guys_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9a%2FThe_Nice_Guys_Poster.jpg&h=0a71ff6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n故事設定於1970年代的洛杉磯，敘述私家偵探侯藍&middot;馬奇（雷恩&middot;葛斯林 飾）受到了脾氣控管不佳的暴力拳擊手傑克森&middot;希利（羅素&middot;克洛 飾）的聘請合作找出失蹤的少女艾蜜莉亞（瑪格麗特&middot;庫利 飾），但在過程中卻又捲入的色情片女星的離奇死亡案件中。在經過調查後，兩人發現一個令人震驚的犯罪陰謀正在醞釀之中"},{"pid":"0f3a38f6a45bb2e1d82606a53f874f0dc1966a7a","tid":667142,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fea7e498bc9a4f1a69271d7cc719471d7d118ce","tid":667142,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T15:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9beda2d85895200ebb06c73a1286a64724ca1e","tid":667142,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T16:57:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}